# gotchas/ — curated by Eratosthenes

Things that will bite you if you don't know about them. Usually surfaced after
someone wastes time on them once. Each entry has: the trap, the symptom you'll
see, and the fix/workaround.

File naming: `<tool-or-area>-<short-tag>.md` (e.g., `extract-lovs-empty-dir-hang.md`).

Do not write to this directory. Submit via Protocol A — see common-prompt.md.
